### Upload Store Info logo (ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/settings/store-info/logo
Content-Type: application/json
X-Staff-Role: ADMIN
X-Staff-Id: demo-admin

{
  "fileDataUrl": "data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAQAAAC1HAwCAAAAC0lEQVR42mP8/x8AAwMCAO+aF9sAAAAASUVORK5CYII="
}

### Remove uploaded Store Info logo (ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/settings/store-info/logo
X-Staff-Role: ADMIN
X-Staff-Id: demo-admin
